        <div class="callout">
          <p><strong>Don't qualify it as a "single dad budget."</strong> A budget is just math. The goal is the same as anyone's: spend less than you make, save something, don't let a bad month wreck you. You don't need to be perfect at it — just consistent.</p>
        </div>

